  <data key="d15">ann.st-ii-ii-q048-a001-resp-concept-domestic-prudence-subjective-part-of-concept-prudence | ann.st-ii-ii-q050-a003-resp-concept-domestic-prudence-subjective-part-of-concept-prudence</data>
